  <description><![CDATA[<p>Nestled in the northern part of <a data-udi="umb://document/cb5fe8e189a14e65a7ffecde5501b6c1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cb5fe8e189a14e65a7ffecde5501b6c1}" title="Nozawa Onsen">Nozawa</a>, the Grand Hotel offers a comfortable retreat after a great day exploring the tree lined runs of Nozawa. Western style rooms feel spacious with twin mattresses on a raised platform. Superior rooms also include a small, private onsen on the balcony. Enjoy breakfast with views towards the pistes, or enjoy the views from the hotels communal onsen which can also be privatised for a fee. Ski lockers are also available in the hotel, or at the gondola station (payable locally).</p>
